#

Creamy Garlic Parmesan Pasta

25 min
$10
600 kcal
Difficulty: 25%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianComfort Food

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

EasyQuickPastaCreamy

Description

A rich and creamy pasta dish with a delightful garlic and parmesan flavor that comes together in no time!

Ingredients

  • pasta: 8 ounces
  • butter: 2 tablespoons
  • garlic (minced): 4 cloves
  • heavy cream: 1 cup
  • parmesan cheese (grated): 1 cup
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • fresh parsley (chopped): for garnish
